{
  "video_id": "0-oudCnIYQw",
  "title": "CA \"Hit & Run\" Laws - A former cop & DA explain",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 240.0,
      "end_time": 2750.0,
      "text": "-Mike, I know you were a cop for 13 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2750.0,
      "end_time": 3929.0,
      "text": "Now you&#39;re a defense lawyer."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 3930.0,
      "end_time": 6990.0,
      "text": "And I know you&#39;re an expert on the area of hit and run and"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6990.0,
      "end_time": 8960.0,
      "text": "hit and run law in California, and I want to"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8960.0,
      "end_time": 9810.0,
      "text": "ask you about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 9810.0,
      "end_time": 11850.0,
      "text": "But let me ask you first of all."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 11850.0,
      "end_time": 14530.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re in an accident in California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 14530.0,
      "end_time": 15840.0,
      "text": "what are your duties?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 15840.0,
      "end_time": 17820.0,
      "text": "What does the law say you have to do afterwards?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 17820.0,
      "end_time": 20580.0,
      "text": "-Well, here in California, we make a little distinction."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 20580.0,
      "end_time": 23490.0,
      "text": "If there&#39;s a traffic accident and there&#39;s property damage"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 23490.0,
      "end_time": 26580.0,
      "text": "only, the requirements are one, either you can report it"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 26580.0,
      "end_time": 29900.0,
      "text": "to the police or minimally exchange information with the"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 29100.0,
      "end_time": 30960.0,
      "text": "other driver or the other property owner."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 30960.0,
      "end_time": 33390.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say, for example, you strike a fence."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 33390.0,
      "end_time": 35250.0,
      "text": "You got to get out, get the information of the property"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 35250.0,
      "end_time": 37310.0,
      "text": "owner, perhaps some way to identify."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 37310.0,
      "end_time": 40715.0,
      "text": "And ultimately, if it&#39;s over $750 worth of damage, report"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 40715.0,
      "end_time": 42430.0,
      "text": "it to the Department of Motor Vehicles."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 42430.0,
      "end_time": 43620.0,
      "text": "-What if the owner is not there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 43620.0,
      "end_time": 46700.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say I scrape a car that&#39;s parked, and I can&#39;t"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 46700.0,
      "end_time": 46760.0,
      "text": "find the owner."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 46760.0,
      "end_time": 47879.0,
      "text": "-I tell people all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 47880.0,
      "end_time": 52600.0,
      "text": "Reasonable efforts to leave the information necessary for"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 52600.0,
      "end_time": 53220.0,
      "text": "you to be identified."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 53220.0,
      "end_time": 55800.0,
      "text": "For example, if that situation happened with me, I would"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 55800.0,
      "end_time": 58650.0,
      "text": "leave my business card or my cell number on"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 58650.0,
      "end_time": 61180.0,
      "text": "the door of the property."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 61180.0,
      "end_time": 63400.0,
      "text": "And I want them to know I was involved in an accident,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 63400.0,
      "end_time": 64129.0,
      "text": "please call me."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 64129.00000000001,
      "end_time": 65910.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s one of the simple ways to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 65910.0,
      "end_time": 68649.0,
      "text": "Now, it changes, though, if in fact there&#39;s an injury."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 68650.0,
      "end_time": 72600.0,
      "text": "If someone is hurt in a traffic accident, your duties"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 72600.0,
      "end_time": 73400.0,
      "text": "are much different."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 73400.0,
      "end_time": 75780.0,
      "text": "Not only do you have to stop, but you have to render"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 75780.0,
      "end_time": 79125.0,
      "text": "reasonable aid and then report it to law enforcement."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 79125.0,
      "end_time": 80110.0,
      "text": "-Now, let me ask you, Mike."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 80110.0,
      "end_time": 83800.0,
      "text": "Is hit and run, is it a misdemeanor or a felony in"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 83800.0,
      "end_time": 83789.0,
      "text": "California?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 83790.0,
      "end_time": 85210.0,
      "text": "-It actually could be both."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 85210.0,
      "end_time": 90130.0,
      "text": "For example, under vehicle section 20002 property damage"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 90130.0,
      "end_time": 92119.0,
      "text": "only would be a misdemeanor."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 92120.0,
      "end_time": 97600.0,
      "text": "However, under vehicle section 20001, if someone is injured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 97600.0,
      "end_time": 100899.0,
      "text": "and you leave the scene without identifying who you"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 100900.0,
      "end_time": 103410.0,
      "text": "are or rendering reasonable aid or staying around until"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 103410.0,
      "end_time": 106390.0,
      "text": "the police arrive< you could be charged as a felony."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 106400.0,
      "end_time": 108200.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s very severe ramifications even."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 108200.0,
      "end_time": 111880.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re charged with a misdemeanor, hit and run"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 111880.0,
      "end_time": 117630.0,
      "text": "causing injury, a violation of 20001 if you admit that"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 117630.0,
      "end_time": 119949.0,
      "text": "allegation or are found guilty, the Department of"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 119950.0,
      "end_time": 122610.0,
      "text": "Motor Vehicle will revoke your driver&#39;s license for a minimum"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 122610.0,
      "end_time": 123820.0,
      "text": "of one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 123820.0,
      "end_time": 125919.0,
      "text": "-What if you didn&#39;t realize there was damage?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 125920.0,
      "end_time": 128300.0,
      "text": "I mean I&#39;ve had calls from people who say there was a"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 128300.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132100.0,
      "text": "fender-bender, and it was sort of a loud street."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 132100.0,
      "end_time": 134790.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t realize that there was contact or damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 134790.0,
      "end_time": 138300.0,
      "text": "But later, the police contacted them and said, well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 138300.0,
      "end_time": 140550.0,
      "text": "somebody reported you for hit and run."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 140550.0,
      "end_time": 142220.0,
      "text": "And apparently, you did cause damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 142220.0,
      "end_time": 144170.0,
      "text": "If didn&#39;t know there was damage, can you still be"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 144170.0,
      "end_time": 145269.0,
      "text": "charged with hit and run?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 145270.0,
      "end_time": 148610.0,
      "text": "-Well, you can be charged with hit and run if the DA believes"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 148610.0,
      "end_time": 149480.0,
      "text": "you did know."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 149480.0,
      "end_time": 150440.0,
      "text": "What the bottom line is this."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 150440.0,
      "end_time": 152900.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an absolute defense to that case."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 152900.0,
      "end_time": 156290.0,
      "text": "If in fact you reasonably didn&#39;t have the facts to"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 156290.0,
      "end_time": 158230.0,
      "text": "believe that you actually struck another vehicle, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 158230.0,
      "end_time": 161700.0,
      "text": "you caused some property damage to someone, there&#39;s no"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 161700.0,
      "end_time": 165350.0,
      "text": "requirement then to report it."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 165350.0,
      "end_time": 167190.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also the totality of circumstances"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 167190.0,
      "end_time": 168359.0,
      "text": "on a case like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 168360.0,
      "end_time": 170280.0,
      "text": "And there are case by case bases."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 170280.0,
      "end_time": 173310.0,
      "text": "And where we see often, at least here, at least in San"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 173310.0,
      "end_time": 176190.0,
      "text": "Bernardino, is we have some ongoing construction of the"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 176190.0,
      "end_time": 179700.0,
      "text": "215 freeway where the lanes are narrowing, and they have"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 179700.0,
      "end_time": 181799.0,
      "text": "these K rails really impeding on the traffic."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 181800.0,
      "end_time": 183570.0,
      "text": "We recently had a case where someone was accused of"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 183570.0,
      "end_time": 184965.0,
      "text": "side-swiping another car."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 184966.0,
      "end_time": 187540.0,
      "text": "Our client really did not know that."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 187540.0,
      "end_time": 190870.0,
      "text": "The DA filed the case anyway based upon the CHP report."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 190870.0,
      "end_time": 193620.0,
      "text": "We were able to gather witness statements from other people"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 193620.0,
      "end_time": 196760.0,
      "text": "in our client&#39;s car, and we showed them to the DA."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 196760.0,
      "end_time": 198302.0,
      "text": "The DA believed those statements, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 198302.0,
      "end_time": 200670.0,
      "text": "our case was dismissed."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 200670.0,
      "end_time": 201410.0,
      "text": "-Let me ask you."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 201410.0,
      "end_time": 203210.0,
      "text": "What if it&#39;s difference dangerous to stop?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 203210.0,
      "end_time": 206100.0,
      "text": "I mean, let&#39;s say you have an accident with someone, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 206100.0,
      "end_time": 207810.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re in sort of a bad neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 207810.0,
      "end_time": 213620.0,
      "text": "And this angry mob starts to gather around, and you feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 213620.0,
      "end_time": 215150.0,
      "text": "that your safety would be threatened."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 215150.0,
      "end_time": 217590.0,
      "text": "That it&#39;s really not safe for you to stop right there at the"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 217590.0,
      "end_time": 219400.0,
      "text": "scene and get out of the car."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 219400.0,
      "end_time": 222600.0,
      "text": "So you drive off somewhere and maybe contact the police."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 222600.0,
      "end_time": 223370.0,
      "text": "But you didn&#39;t stop right away."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 223370.0,
      "end_time": 224510.0,
      "text": "Is that a defense?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 224510.0,
      "end_time": 226170.0,
      "text": "Can you be prosecuted in that case?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 226170.0,
      "end_time": 227299.0,
      "text": "-That is a defense."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 227300.0,
      "end_time": 232710.0,
      "text": "And actually, I tell my own daughter, who&#39;s now 26, if"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 232710.0,
      "end_time": 235670.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re an accident in an area that you&#39;re unfamiliar with or"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 235670.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re worried about, it&#39;s dark, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 238859.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re out there alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 238860.0,
      "end_time": 241570.0,
      "text": "If your cell phone&#39;s not working, to leave that area."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 241570.0,
      "end_time": 244769.0,
      "text": "Find the closest phone you can get to, and then call the"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 244770.0,
      "end_time": 247466.0,
      "text": "accident in."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 247466.0,
      "end_time": 250420.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s good advice for anybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 250420.0,
      "end_time": 253490.0,
      "text": "And that actually would lead to a defense, and we often"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 253500.0,
      "end_time": 253820.0,
      "text": "have cases like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 253820.0,
      "end_time": 256950.0,
      "text": "Currently, we have a case up in the Victorville courthouse"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 256950.0,
      "end_time": 260860.0,
      "text": "where our client was driving down a lonely road, late at"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 260860.0,
      "end_time": 261980.0,
      "text": "night, struck something."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 261980.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264380.0,
      "text": "She believed she struck a coyote."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 264380.0,
      "end_time": 265980.0,
      "text": "She continued on."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 265980.0,
      "end_time": 268300.0,
      "text": "She didn&#39;t have her cellphone with her."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 268300.0,
      "end_time": 270120.0,
      "text": "She did not have her cell phone with her."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 270120.0,
      "end_time": 272690.0,
      "text": "Stopped at the next available place, which was around 10"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 272690.0,
      "end_time": 275469.0,
      "text": "miles away, called her mom."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 275470.0,
      "end_time": 277570.0,
      "text": "Her mother said, don&#39;t worry about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 277570.0,
      "end_time": 278250.0,
      "text": "Just come home."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 278250.0,
      "end_time": 280360.0,
      "text": "When you get home, we&#39;ll call the police."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 280360.0,
      "end_time": 282620.0,
      "text": "She drove another 30 miles to her house."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 282620.0,
      "end_time": 284705.0,
      "text": "About two hours go by, they call the police."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 284705.0,
      "end_time": 286190.0,
      "text": "The police say, don&#39;t worry about, it&#39;s not our"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 286190.0,
      "end_time": 287440.0,
      "text": "jurisdiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 287440.0,
      "end_time": 290140.0,
      "text": "And the next day, the CHP are investigating an accident"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 290140.0,
      "end_time": 291460.0,
      "text": "when, actually, it wasn&#39;t a coyote."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 291460.0,
      "end_time": 293150.0,
      "text": "But it was a person."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 293150.0,
      "end_time": 298700.0,
      "text": "And in that case, they charged her with felony hit and run."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 298700.0,
      "end_time": 300240.0,
      "text": "And that case is currently in litigation, and our defense is"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 300240.0,
      "end_time": 301750.0,
      "text": "exactly that--"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 301750.0,
      "end_time": 303240.0,
      "text": "-She didn&#39;t know that anyone was injured."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 303240.0,
      "end_time": 304970.0,
      "text": "-She didn&#39;t know that anyone was injured."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 304970.0,
      "end_time": 307690.0,
      "text": "It was reasonable to believe that she struck a coyote in"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 307690.0,
      "end_time": 311980.0,
      "text": "this remote area in the desert and that she did you go home"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 311980.0,
      "end_time": 312770.0,
      "text": "and report it."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 312770.0,
      "end_time": 314570.0,
      "text": "But the police didn&#39;t want to take the report because she"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 314570.0,
      "end_time": 317380.0,
      "text": "had left the jurisdiction from one agency to another."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 317380.0,
      "end_time": 319540.0,
      "text": "-What about improving the crime?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 319540.0,
      "end_time": 323980.0,
      "text": "I mean, is it enough for the DA to show that it was my car"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 323980.0,
      "end_time": 324680.0,
      "text": "in a hit and run?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 324680.0,
      "end_time": 326670.0,
      "text": "Or do they have show I was a driver?"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 326670.0,
      "end_time": 329400.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say my car is involved in a hit and run accident this"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 329400.0,
      "end_time": 331909.0,
      "text": "morning, and someone takes down the plate."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 331910.0,
      "end_time": 335700.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very clearly my car, but no one sees who&#39;s driving."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 335700.0,
      "end_time": 337930.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t have any evidence that I was the one driving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 337930.0,
      "end_time": 339460.0,
      "text": "and potentially, someone else could have"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 339460.0,
      "end_time": 340870.0,
      "text": "been driving my car."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 340870.0,
      "end_time": 342870.0,
      "text": "Is that enough for the DA to make their case?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 342870.0,
      "end_time": 344960.0,
      "text": "Or do they have to show I was the one actually behind the"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 344960.0,
      "end_time": 345239.0,
      "text": "wheel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 345240.0,
      "end_time": 345940.0,
      "text": "-Well, certainly."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 345940.0,
      "end_time": 348410.0,
      "text": "DAs make cases like we do building blocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 348410.0,
      "end_time": 350310.0,
      "text": "Just like we defend cases, knocking down"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 350310.0,
      "end_time": 351370.0,
      "text": "the building blocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 351370.0,
      "end_time": 354350.0,
      "text": "And part of it is they can&#39;t just prove that their vehicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 354350.0,
      "end_time": 354980.0,
      "text": "was involved."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 354980.0,
      "end_time": 357270.0,
      "text": "They need to prove who the actual driver was."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 357270.0,
      "end_time": 360440.0,
      "text": "And in this day and age, unfortunately, for people that"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 360440.0,
      "end_time": 362920.0,
      "text": "do exercise some poor judgment in that momentary minute of"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 362920.0,
      "end_time": 364720.0,
      "text": "time, there&#39;s lots of additional"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 364720.0,
      "end_time": 366160.0,
      "text": "resources now for the DAs."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 366160.0,
      "end_time": 369390.0,
      "text": "We have these light cameras that take a picture of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 369390.0,
      "end_time": 372440.0,
      "text": "three blocks away, or new vehicles have the"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 372440.0,
      "end_time": 373400.0,
      "text": "black boxes in them."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 373400.0,
      "end_time": 376200.0,
      "text": "They follow you, and people will call on their cell phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 376200.0,
      "end_time": 380130.0,
      "text": "And the police do a really great job modernly of tracking"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 380130.0,
      "end_time": 382640.0,
      "text": "down people through these scientific means to find out"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 382640.0,
      "end_time": 385490.0,
      "text": "right after the accident, your phone was called your mother&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 385490.0,
      "end_time": 388600.0,
      "text": "number from a cell site two blocks from"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 388600.0,
      "end_time": 389160.0,
      "text": "the accident scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 389160.0,
      "end_time": 391900.0,
      "text": "So there are ways for them, absent of an eyewitness"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 391900.0,
      "end_time": 395390.0,
      "text": "saying, yes, that&#39;s the person who was driving, modernly, to"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 395400.0,
      "end_time": 396800.0,
      "text": "try to put you behind the wheel of that car."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 396800.0,
      "end_time": 399240.0,
      "text": "-But at the end of the day, before they can convict me of"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 399240.0,
      "end_time": 401130.0,
      "text": "hit and run, they have to prove I was the one driving."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 401130.0,
      "end_time": 402500.0,
      "text": "-Absolutely."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 402500.0,
      "end_time": 405410.0,
      "text": "They have to be able to convince a jury of 12 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 405410.0,
      "end_time": 408490.0,
      "text": "that not only was it your car involved in that accident, but"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 408490.0,
      "end_time": 410160.0,
      "text": "you were the driver."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 410160.0,
      "end_time": 411600.0,
      "text": "-Now, let me ask you this."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 411600.0,
      "end_time": 416760.0,
      "text": "I get calls, periodically, from people who say, listen, I"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 416760.0,
      "end_time": 419849.0,
      "text": "was contacted by the CHP, either on the phone or a voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 419850.0,
      "end_time": 423260.0,
      "text": "mail or letter, and says you&#39;re a person of interest in"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 423260.0,
      "end_time": 425600.0,
      "text": "a hit and run incident."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 425600.0,
      "end_time": 426160.0,
      "text": "We want to interview."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 426160.0,
      "end_time": 427710.0,
      "text": "We need to come down to the station."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 427710.0,
      "end_time": 429710.0,
      "text": "We need you to contact this detective."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 429710.0,
      "end_time": 432685.0,
      "text": "Should they go contact detective on their own?"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 432685.0,
      "end_time": 434150.0,
      "text": "-Absolutely not."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 434150.0,
      "end_time": 436679.0,
      "text": "We handle many cases a year like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 436680.0,
      "end_time": 440370.0,
      "text": "And what we do is we&#39;ll open up this case for these folks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 440370.0,
      "end_time": 443910.0,
      "text": "what we call it pre-filing investigative case."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 443910.0,
      "end_time": 447670.0,
      "text": "And what we&#39;ll do is we&#39;ll independently investigate the"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 447670.0,
      "end_time": 450390.0,
      "text": "accident with the attorney-client privilege."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 450390.0,
      "end_time": 452229.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll find out what&#39;s going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 452230.0,
      "end_time": 456120.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll contact law enforcement and find out where they are in"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 456120.0,
      "end_time": 458250.0,
      "text": "the case, confirm some information."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 458250.0,
      "end_time": 460610.0,
      "text": "And eventually, while we&#39;ll tell the police our client"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 460610.0,
      "end_time": 462530.0,
      "text": "will always be cooperative, the truth of"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 462530.0,
      "end_time": 463780.0,
      "text": "the matter is this."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 463780.0,
      "end_time": 467100.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a rare occasion that we&#39;ll allow someone to give a"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 467100.0,
      "end_time": 468390.0,
      "text": "statement to police."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 468390.0,
      "end_time": 469700.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s aberrational."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 469700.0,
      "end_time": 471450.0,
      "text": "It happens occasionally."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 471450.0,
      "end_time": 472940.0,
      "text": "Everything&#39;s on a case-by-case basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 472940.0,
      "end_time": 475740.0,
      "text": "But for the most part, it&#39;s a rare occasion that we&#39;ll allow"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 475740.0,
      "end_time": 479800.0,
      "text": "a client to speak to law enforcement in a situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 479800.0,
      "end_time": 479640.0,
      "text": "like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 479640.0,
      "end_time": 481810.0,
      "text": "-So absolutely don&#39;t call the police back."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 481810.0,
      "end_time": 484780.0,
      "text": "Call your attorney and let your attorney handle it."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 484780.0,
      "end_time": 486260.0,
      "text": "-Perfectly said."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 486260.0,
      "end_time": 488700.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s exactly what you should do."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 488700.0,
      "end_time": 491390.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m Mike Scaffidi, a retired police officer and now a"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 491390.0,
      "end_time": 493770.0,
      "text": "criminal defense attorney with Shouse Law Group."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 493770.0,
      "end_time": 495490.0,
      "text": "If you or a loved one are in trouble and"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 495490.0,
      "end_time": 496860.0,
      "text": "need help, call me."
    }
  ]
}